PrecisApprove the authorization for DR. PATABENDI KORALALAGE ABEYTUNGA, of Dundas, Ontario, Vice-President of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety, to act as President of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety, effective December 30, 1996, until the office of President of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety is no longer vacant.
